 * End
 * Promise 1 Fulfilled
 * Promise 1 Then Fulfilled
 * Timer 1
 * Timer 2 in Promise 2
 * Promise 2 Then 1
 * Promise 2 Then 2
 * Timer 3 in Promise 1
 */
```

解析：

